title: Sid Meiers Civilization VI Deluxe Edition All DLC
description:
About This Game

Civilization VI offers new ways to engage with your world: cities now physically expand across the map, active research in technology and culture unlocks new potential, and competing leaders will pursue their own agendas based on their historical traits as you race for one of five ways to achieve victory in the game.

Digital Deluxe Extras
Aztec Civilization Pack 
25th Anniversary Soundtrack
Civilization VI - Poland Civilization & Scenario Pack
Civilization VI - Vikings Scenario Pack
Civilization VI - Australia Civilization & Scenario Pack
Civilization VI - Persia & Macedon Civilization

Install:
1) Install the game
2) Play the game

If you enjoy the game remember to buy it. :)
